{"tid":1814283,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武退埸／捉鬼論?","createTime":"2020-01-07T00:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T05:56:01.000Z","uid":53515,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9308b36c7a990b025e5be83db2f8cae6b810520c","tid":1814283,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:37:53.000Z","msg":"救理大，十萬和理非都豁出去，你仲話和理非捉鬼搞到勇武退？<br />\n根本理大傷到仆街，依家狗隻只係放風搞心理戰，想軟化剩低嘅勇武，點解咁容易打稻草人？<br />\n<br />\n我只會話不割<br />\n<br />\n利申：冇捉鬼，怕捉錯，但成日被鬼纏繞"},{"pid":"67b50ab5974ab120b8f4c959e24187cb062eb286","tid":1814283,"uid":53515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:38:36.000Z","msg":"我都係勇武，但你哋捉鬼捉到我唔落埸喇～"},{"pid":"17673a9aaa53f2b744dfbed4b5da16bfdeb84fd1","tid":1814283,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1a8809fea8836ad29ca259ce36fce430d82012","tid":1814283,"uid":102700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:41:59.000Z","msg":"一開始個時又話勇武要等和理非走 <br />\n和理非又等勇武走 <br />\n結果兩邊唔走塞住勇武俾人拉<br />\n<br />\n依家又話和理非散場就走搞到務武俾人拉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4245e504d580baba822d335e99907f2dee10323d","tid":1814283,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67b50ab5974ab120b8f4c959e24187cb062eb286","tid":1814283,"uid":53515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:38:36.000Z","msg":"我都係勇武，但你哋捉鬼捉到我唔落埸喇～"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:02:50.000Z","msg":"你網上勇武咋<br />\n你邊有落過場呀"},{"pid":"c0e836b3f44c9ac587960071cfbc9871a5a8bba4","tid":1814283,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4245e504d580baba822d335e99907f2dee10323d","tid":1814283,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67b50ab5974ab120b8f4c959e24187cb062eb286","tid":1814283,"uid":53515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01